<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>TransitCloud Developers — API & Recipes</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Developer portal for TransitCloud: API patterns, SDK placeholders, proof bundle schema, verification recipes, and integration guidance." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container topbar__inner">
      <a class="brand" href="./index.html">
        <span class="brand__mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="brand__name">TransitCloud</span>
        <span class="brand__tag">Developers</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="./index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="./docs.html">Docs</a>
        <a class="is-active" href="./developers.html">Developers</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="topbar__cta">
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="#recipes">Recipes</a>
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="#api">API Reference</a>
        <button class="iconbtn" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Toggle theme" title="Toggle theme">◐</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="pageHead">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Developer Portal</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Integrate TransitCloud into apps, services, and custody rails. Verify documents locally, or anchor roots onchain.
        </p>

        <div class="pillRow">
          <span class="pill">Canonical JSON</span>
          <span class="pill">SHA-256</span>
          <span class="pill">Ed25519</span>
          <span class="pill">Proof Bundles</span>
          <span class="pill">Receipts</span>
          <span class="pill">Optional Anchors</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="api">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__head">
          <h2>API Reference (Blueprint)</h2>
          <p>These endpoints define a clean, production-friendly interface. Adjust names to match your implementation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="apiGrid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/canonize</h3>
            <p>Canonicalize document JSON.</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "doc": { "type": "invoice", "version": "DOC.USD.v1", "body": { } },
  "canon": { "ruleset": "canon.v1" }
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns canonical bytes (or canonical JSON) + metadata.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/hash</h3>
            <p>Generate SHA-256 root from canonical bytes.</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "canonical": "base64(...)" 
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns hex root + algorithm + byteLength.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/sign</h3>
            <p>Sign canonical bytes (Ed25519).</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "canonical": "base64(...)",
  "keyRef": "issuer-key-1"
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns signature + key fingerprint.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/verify</h3>
            <p>Verify proof bundle.</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "bundle": { "root": "hex", "signatures": [], "doc": {} }
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns verification report + failures list.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/bundle</h3>
            <p>Create portable proof bundle.</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "doc": {},
  "root": "hex",
  "signatures": []
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns bundle JSON + bundle hash.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>POST /v1/anchor (optional)</h3>
            <p>Write root hash to chain (attestation).</p>
            <pre><code>{
  "root": "hex",
  "network": "base",
  "mode": "attest"
}</code></pre>
            <div class="muted">Returns tx hash + block reference.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--alt" id="recipes">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__head">
          <h2>Verification Recipes</h2>
          <p>Copy/paste patterns for auditors, integrators, and partners.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="card card--code">
            <h3>Recipe: verify a bundle</h3>
            <pre><code>1) bytes = canonicalize(bundle.doc, ruleset)
2) root  = sha256(bytes)
3) assert(root == bundle.root)

4) for sig in bundle.signatures:
     assert(ed25519_verify(sig.pubkey, bytes, sig.signature))

5) report OK</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="card card--code">
            <h3>Recipe: generate a receipt</h3>
            <pre><code>receipt = {
  "eventId": "uuid",
  "root": "hex",
  "action": "INGEST|TRANSFER|ARCHIVE",
  "timestamp": "ISO-8601",
  "actor": { "id": "issuer", "pubkeyFp": "..." }
}
receiptSig = ed25519_sign(canonicalize(receipt), actorPrivKey)</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Recommended invariants</h3>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li>Canonicalization rules are versioned and immutable per version.</li>
              <li>Signature binds to canonical bytes, not parsed JSON.</li>
              <li>All custody writes are idempotent by eventId.</li>
              <li>Anchoring never publishes sensitive contents.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>SDK plan (placeholders)</h3>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li><strong>@transitcloud/sdk-js</strong> — browser + node</li>
              <li><strong>@transitcloud/sdk-python</strong> — audit tooling</li>
              <li><strong>@transitcloud/cli</strong> — canonize/hash/sign/verify/bundle</li>
            </ul>
            <a class="link" href="./docs.html#spec">Spec reference →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="status">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="callout">
          <div class="callout__copy">
            <h2>Production readiness checklist</h2>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li>Formalize spec versions and publish changelog</li>
              <li>Test vectors for canonicalization + hashing</li>
              <li>Key management policy + rotation plan</li>
              <li>Verification report format for auditors</li>
              <li>Pilot scope + disclosure language</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="callout__cta">
            <a class="btn btn--primary" href="./index.html#contact">Generate outreach email</a>
            <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="./docs.html#sandbox">Sandbox packet</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer__grid">
      <div>
        <div class="footer__brand">TransitCloud</div>
        <div class="footer__sub">Developer Portal — API, recipes, integrations</div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__links">
        <a href="./docs.html">Docs</a>
        <a href="./index.html#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__meta">
        <div>© <span id="year"></span> Kam Swygert</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="./app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
